channel.title: Gone Girl
channel.desc: Thriller 2014 Nick's life seems perfect, until his wife Amy goes missing on the day they should be celebrating five years of marriage. With every clue pointing to him, Nick becomes the main suspect. However, nothing, not even their marriage, is as it appears. Ben Affleck, Rosamund Pike, Neil Patrick Harris, Tyler Perry, Carrie Coon, David Fincher, Gillian Flynn.
